caption.p: Histological profiles of liver cells in 6 rat cohorts with 10× magnification in focus assay: (a) healthy control; (b) hepatotoxic control showed massive inflammation liver cells; (c) silymarin control at 200 mg/kg indicated inflammation liver cells; (d) P. odoratissimus extract of 300 mg/kg; (e) P. odoratissimus extract of 600 mg/kg; (f) P. odoratissimus extract of 900 mg/kg. Subfigures (d)–(f) demonstrated the healing of liver cells after the extract treatments towards paracetamol intoxication.
